subject: ENGLISH
text: Describe and comment on the part played by the Clown in any one of Shakespeare’s plays. Or take any one of the following pairs of characters and draw a contrast between them: Falstaff and Prince Hal, Brutus and Cassius, Hamlet and Horatio, Macbeth and Lady Macbeth, Ariel and Caliban. Or what light do the plays of Shakespeare which you have read throw on his character?
